double InitialBillAmount
double FinalBill
char Type
int i

            for (i=0; i<20; i++)

            Read InitialBillAmount

            Read Type

            switch (Type)

            Case F:
FinalBill = InitialBillAmount – (InitialBillAmount * 0.20)

            Case R:
FinalBill = InitialBillAmount – (InitialBillAmount * 0.15)
Add free sample to cart

            Case C:
FinalBill = InitialBillAmount – (InitialBillAmount * 0.10)
Attach free coupon for next order

            Print FinalBill

            End switch

            End for

            Print “You have received a discount. Thank you for shopping with us.”

